        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A bright, octagonal frame surrounds this circular mithral shield, which itself is polished to a mirrorlike sheen that reflects clear and true. While you have this standard-grade mithral shield (Hardness 5, HP 20, BT 10) raised, you gain its circumstance bonus to saving throws against spells with the evil or negative trait.",
